13 Hours Ago For the primary election appeal committee, Chris Baywood Ibe was named the Chairman while Abdulmumini Okara would serve as the Secretary. The other members of the appeal committee include Festus Fientes, Okon Owoefiak, Abba Isah, Umar Duhu, Sani El-katuzu, Osuere Eunice and Emeka Agaba. The committee will be inaugurated on Friday.